{
  "texts": [
    "To provide benchmark comparisons, tricubic interpolation and an image processing-based pipeline were used.",
    "The image processing pipeline included multiple subsequent filters prior to the binary thresholding (anisotropic diffusion, contrast stretching, median filter).",
    "The results were compared using Pearson correlation.",
    "The 95% confidence intervals were estimated for the models that are trained on multiple random seeds.",
    "Finally, Bland-Altman analysis was conducted for the prediction of BV/ TV using the reference methods and the best-performing super-resolution model."
  ]
}